issue.title: Question about asn1tools usage
issue.body:
Hello,

as the author of [asn1tools](https://github.com/eerimoq/asn1tools) I'm interested in why the conversion from UPER to JSON does not work in [scripts/map-data.sh](https://github.com/jauntywunderkind/traffic-light-headsup/blob/3d8d81cc72aacf0643dfcd5f5bfbf0bd5882bc54/scripts/map-data.sh#L23-L30). Is there anything missing in asn1tools?

Unfortunately I do not have access to J2735.asn. =/

issue.title: Scraper AND UI components.
issue.body:
This is the scraper script. Should work as a module. If not `scraper.py` works as a standalone thing.   
Not included is the write to the database, which is essentially  

```
for json_dictionary in system_configuration_web_request_generator(keys):
            cursor.execute('INSERT INTO controller_configurations (info) VALUES (''\'' + json.dumps(json_dictionary ) + '\')')

```
